<title>Zion Chate Zalenna Ding</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Leisiet puon-In kiph7eltha mahleh,
 Khawpi hawihtak mai chu ken ka nei nai;
 Pathien in A siem, Zion chate lenna,
 Zie chu ka kumsawt In.

[V2]
 Zion chate zalenna ding ni chu a naitai,
 Na telna dem Aw suohpih?
 Vaigei leh chun kumsawt kawt kihawn huomlo ding,
 Damlai hinkhuo Lalpa a di'n pieu in.

[V3]
 2. Lei lungngaihna'n hun puimang khana,
 Damlai nikhuo utchak thil a tam ie;
 Pakbang I hinkhuo muolliem ding kuon cha hin,
 Lalpa na sem hitiu.

[V4]
 3. Nitum kuon vai-chieh phat ahi tai,
 Angelte leh mithieng chieh masate'n;
 Khuongpi leh baja tawh eina ngak zing ui,
 Vana kilamtuoh di'n.

[V5]
 4. Lalpa Krista lalna gam achun,
 Leng leh lal chagah gimthei umtalo;
 Tunkal ka ngaklah Zion chate lenna,
 Zie chu ka kumsawt In.</lyrics>
</song>